Sporotrichosis via cat scratch - Brazil 20010820.1966

Re: [We would be interested to know if there are additional documented
animals that have transmitted this infection to humans. - Mods.ES/DS
[1
Date: Wed 22 Aug 2001
From: Christoph Schulze <Christoph.Schulze@svla-ff.brandenburg.de>

Citation: Amaya-Tapia G, Uribe-Jimenez E, Diaz-Perez R, Covarrubias-Velasco
MA, Diaz-Santana-Bustamante D, Aguirre-Avalos G, et al. Sporotrichosis
transmitted by badger bite. Esporotricosis cutanea transmitida por
mordedura de tejon. Medicina-Cutanea-Ibero-Latino-Americana 1996; 24(2): 87-9.
